![E198.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1633477187521-CDUU3YJCLQSTN32LE0WN/E198.jpg)

Sony is hell-bent on knocking their Sony Spider-Man Universe out of the park and Venom: Let There Be Carnage is next at-bat. With Tom Hardy, Woody Harrelson, Naomi Harris, and the first-time cinematic meetup of Venom and Carnage, do they have what it takes to make Venom 2 a home run? Join us as we discuss what amounts to a post-credit scene with a movie attached and try our best to predict what happens next in this Venom 2 recap and review!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
